<1.4>
- Fixed item usage system.
<1.3>
- Changed
- Balloon-Relative Movement System
- Movement is now relative to the direction the balloon is facing.
- W/S Front/Back of the balloon (no longer fixed North/South)
- A/D Left/Right of the balloon (no longer fixed West/East)
- Allows natural control always moves in the visual direction of the balloon.
- Rotation System
- Added rotation control with ALT key.
- Allows rotating the balloon on its own axis.
- Texts, buttons, and speed open for configuration.
- Benefits
- Intuitive control balloon responds to visual direction.
- No need to mentally compensate for orientation.
- Fine speed adjustment without editing code.
- Translatable/customizable prompt texts.
<1.2>
- Fix minor bugs
- Added button configs
<1.1>
- Added items to change status of nearby balloon
